crosoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;js_darkmode__0&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: center; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">\n          <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com onekey\" style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular,PingFangTC-Light,微软雅黑;\" data-pm-slice=\"7 4 []\">\n           <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjtlq1ergzg\" style=\"padding:0px;text-size-adjust:inherit;margin:0px 0px 24px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__25\">\n            <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n             <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:48px 0px 0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;line-height:1.6em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-indent:0em;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__26\"><span style=\"padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-size:50px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\" class=\"js_darkmode__27\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">01</span></span></strong></span></p>\n             <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.578px;clear:both;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.6em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-indent:0em;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__29\"><span style=\"padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\" class=\"js_darkmode__30\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkwjukis1ktx\" style=\"font-size: 17px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkwjukj4x6\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\">背景及现状</span></span></strong></span></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div data-pm-slice=\"6 2 []\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);padding:0px;text-size-adjust:inherit;margin:24px 0px 0px;font-weight:normal;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;line-height:1.6em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__32\">\n           <div style=\"margin: 10px auto;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;transform-style: preserve-3d;box-sizing: border-box !important;\">\n             <div style=\"margin: -35px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;transform: translateZ(10px);box-sizing: border-box !important;\">\n              <div style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;\">\n               <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);z-index:0;text-size-adjust:inherit;font-weight:normal;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;transform:translateZ(10px);outline:0px;overflow:hidden;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;padding:0px;margin:0px 15px;visibility:visible;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.578px;display:flex;transform-style:preserve-3d;line-height:1.6em;max-width:100%;justify-content:center;align-items:center;user-select:text;\"><span class=\"js_darkmode__33\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:黑体, SimHei, STHeiti;\">为了系统地统一当前分散的布局生成任务领域，布局生成旨在为给定的元素设计吸引人的视觉排版，涵盖从海报和文档设计到用户界面布局和杂志排版等广泛任务。虽然生成模型取得了显著进展，但现有方法通常专注于狭义任务，导致解决方案缺乏灵活性和普适性。此外，尽管现有的评估指标基于布局设计原则精心设计，但它们常常与人类的感知不一致。如图1所示，高评分的布局可能在视觉质量上较差，这揭示了现有指标与真实人类感知之间的差距。为了解决这些挑战，我们提出了Uni-Layout，一个通过统一生成器、模拟人类的评估器和动态边距对齐机制来整合布局生成、评估和对齐的整体框架。为了详细阐述Uni-Layout，本文围绕三个核心研究问题展开。</span></span></p>\n              </div>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <p style=\"margin-left: 15px;margin-right: 15px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:黑体, SimHei, STHeiti;\" class=\"js_darkmode__22\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder js_darkmode__23\" data-ratio=\"0.47962962962962963\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);background-color:transparent;text-size-adjust:auto;font-weight:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c6f8a04e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FMrFJyDNenFicK62lpA5M8vwjDupb7Re4s4hqjtnWPibk0dvnbrBCGPIr7Os1zqtWe5FtZm83EtMK7EDWYf2NiaRIw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D0\"></span></span></p>\n       <p style=\"margin-left: 15px;margin-right: 15px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:黑体, SimHei, STHeiti;\" class=\"js_darkmode__24\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkwju0edwa2\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkwju0ek253a\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">图1：布局生成任务的分类体系与动机阐述</span></span></p>\n       <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com onekey\" style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular,PingFangTC-Light,微软雅黑;\" data-pm-slice=\"7 4 []\">\n        <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjtlq1ergzg\" style=\"padding:0px;text-size-adjust:inherit;margin:0px 0px 24px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__25\">\n         <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n          <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:48px 0px 0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;line-height:1.6em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-indent:0em;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__26\"><span style=\"padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-size:50px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\" class=\"js_darkmode__27\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">02</span></span></strong></span></p>\n          <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.578px;clear:both;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.6em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-indent:0em;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__29\"><span style=\"padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\" class=\"js_darkmode__30\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkwjukis1ktx\" style=\"font-size: 17px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkwjukj4x6\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\">如何实现跨任务的统一布局生成</span></span></strong></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div data-pm-slice=\"6 2 []\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);padding:0px;text-size-adjust:inherit;margin:24px 0px 0px;font-weight:normal;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;line-height:1.6em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__32\">\n        <div style=\"margin: 10px auto;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n         <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;transform-style: preserve-3d;box-sizing: border-box !important;\">\n          <div style=\"margin: -35px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;transform: translateZ(10px);box-sizing: border-box !important;\">\n           <div style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;\">\n            <p style=\"margin: 0px 15px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;line-height: 1.6em;box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:黑体, SimHei, STHeiti;\" class=\"js_darkmode__33\"><span leaf=\"\">为了系统地统一当前分散的布局生成任务领域，我们提出了一个基于两个维度的精心组织的分类法：背景和元素内容是自由的还是受限的。如图1所示，我们将现有的布局任务分为四种代表性类型：BFEF、BCEF、BFEC和BCEC。当前的任务特定方法在统一布局生成方面存在困难，但多模态大型语言模型（MLLMs）由于其通用的视觉-语言理解能力，提供了有前景的解决方案。利用MLLMs，我们提出了一个统一的布局生成器，其工作方式类似于一名熟练的设计师。该生成器结合视觉约束和文本指令来生成连贯的布局，能够处理背景和元素内容既可以受限也可以自由的多种场景。通过在各种布局任务上的联合训练，它为布局生成提供了一个灵活且统一的解决方案。</span></span></p>\n            <p style=\"margin: 0px 15px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;line-height: 1.6em;box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:黑体, SimHei, STHeiti;\" class=\"js_darkmode__35\"><span leaf=\"\">为了统一多种布局任务，一个通用的布局任务指令可写作：</span></span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder js_darkmo